snippet.title: Resident Evil 2 - E3 2018 Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
In 4K where available! Itching for more Resident Evil 2 gameplay? We’ve got fresh video for you to sink your teeth into. Pre-order now, and play Resident Evil 2 as soon as it's available on January 25th, 2019.
